>(or approaches but never reaches 2).  Would it be safe to say that 
no 
>matter how close the left side of the equation approaches 2 it will 
>fall infinitely short of number 2?  If this is so, would it be 
>accurate to say that 1 + 1/2 + 1/4 ... (ad infinitum) = 2 - (an 
